parameters: \nc<Saki>Ugh, I feel like I'm dying from this hangover...

\nc<Saki>I ended up sleeping on the floor instead of the bed... I
definitely drank too much last night.

\bustMsgExpression[1, 0]\nc<Saki>What's that? It's been really bothering me for a while
now...
\nc<Saki>What on earth is this!? A tail!?

\nc<Saki>Why do I have a tail!? Did everyone play a prank on me
yesterday!?
\nc<Saki>...That's right! The hospital! I have to go to the hospital!

\nc<Saki>Logically speaking, humans can't just grow tails! This has
to be some kind of mistake!!
